  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-02 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors are assessed. The package decision is Accepted on the basis of compensating evidence and expert judgment, though one factor (Model inputs) carries an achieved level below the required level. The shortfall is acknowledged in narrative but is not formally resolved.",
