      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must hold ISO 9001 certification or equivalent; version control, regression testing, and release documentation must be current.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 is deployed under a validated software environment with ISO 9001-certified QMS at the simulation facility. Version-controlled solver binaries, regression test suite (1,847 test cases, 100% pass rate for release), and formal change-control documentation satisfy MRL 5 requirements. Software qualification report SQR-2022-07 on file."
    },
    {
