      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal code verification against manufactured solutions or published benchmarks with documented order-of-accuracy confirmation.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver module. Observed spatial order of accuracy: 1.97 (target ≥1.8). Temporal order: 1.93. Benchmark comparisons against FDA nozzle and lid-driven cavity canonical cases show residuals consistent with published reference data. Code verification report CVR-2022-11 archived."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
